@host = http://localhost:5000
@contentType = application/json

### ==================== VARIABLES ====================
### Store tokens and IDs here after successful requests
@adminToken = 
@studentToken = 
@admindId = 1
@studentId = 2
@applicationId = 1

### ==================== PUBLIC ENDPOINTS ====================

### 1. Health Check - API Running
GET {{host}}/

### ==================== AUTH ROUTES (/api/auth) ====================

### 2. Signup - First user becomes ADMIN
POST {{host}}/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "admin@eduequity.com",
  "password": "Admin@123",
  "full_name": "Admin User"
}

### 3. Signup - Register a Student
POST {{host}}/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "student1@eduequity.com",
  "password": "Student@123",
  "full_name": "John Kipchoge",
  "national_id": "12345678",
  "institution": "University of Nairobi",
  "course": "Computer Science",
  "year_of_study": 2
}

### 4. Login - Admin Login
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "admin@eduequity.com",
  "password": "Admin@123"
}

### 5. Login - Student Login
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "student1@eduequity.com",
  "password": "Student@123"
}

### 6. Forgot Password
POST {{host}}/api/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "student1@eduequity.com"
}

### 7. Reset Password
POST {{host}}/api/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "student1@eduequity.com",
  "token": "reset-token-from-email",
  "newPassword": "NewPassword@123"
}

### ==================== STUDENTS ROUTES (/api/students) ====================

### 8. Student Register (Alternative to Auth Signup)
POST {{host}}/api/students/register/student
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "student2@eduequity.com",
  "password": "Student@123",
  "full_name": "Grace Mwangi",
  "national_id": "87654321",
  "institution": "Kenyatta University",
  "course": "Business Administration",
  "year_of_study": 3
}

### 9. Get Student Profile
GET {{host}}/api/students/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{studentToken}}

### 10. Update Student Profile
PUT {{host}}/api/students/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{studentToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "full_name": "John Kipchoge Updated",
  "institution": "University of Nairobi",
  "course": "Computer Science",
  "year_of_study": 3
}

### ==================== USERS ROUTES (/api/users) ====================

### 11. Register Admin User (Admin Only)
POST {{host}}/api/users/admin
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "admin2@eduequity.com",
  "password": "Admin@123",
  "full_name": "Second Admin"
}

### ==================== REGISTER ROUTES (/api/register) ====================

### 12. Admin Registers New Student (Admin Only)
POST {{host}}/api/register/
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "student3@eduequity.com",
  "password": "Student@123",
  "role": "STUDENT",
  "full_name": "David Ochieng",
  "national_id": "11111111",
  "institution": "Mount Kenya University",
  "course": "Engineering",
  "year_of_study": 1
}

### 12b. Admin Registers New Admin (Admin Only)
POST {{host}}/api/register/
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "admin3@eduequity.com",
  "password": "Admin@123",
  "role": "ADMIN",
  "full_name": "Third Admin"
}

### ==================== APPLICATIONS ROUTES (/api/applications) ====================

### 13. Submit Application with Documents (Student Only)
### Note: This requires multipart/form-data. Use REST Client extension to upload files.
POST {{host}}/api/applications/
Authorization: Bearer {{studentToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="cycle_year"

2026
------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="amount_requested"

50000
------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="documents"; filename="document.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./sample-document.pdf
------WebKitFormBoundary--

### 13b. Submit Application Without Documents (Simplified)
POST {{host}}/api/applications/
Authorization: Bearer {{studentToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "cycle_year": 2026,
  "amount_requested": 50000
}

### 14. Get My Applications (Student Only)
GET {{host}}/api/applications/my-applications
Authorization: Bearer {{studentToken}}

### 15. Get All Applications (Admin/Committee Only)
GET {{host}}/api/applications/
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 16. Get All Applications with Status Filter
GET {{host}}/api/applications/?status=PENDING
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 17. Get Audit Logs for Application (Admin Only)
GET {{host}}/api/applications/1/audit-logs
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 18. Approve Application (Admin Only)
PATCH {{host}}/api/applications/1/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "status": "APPROVED",
  "amount_allocated": 50000
}

### 19. Reject Application (Admin Only)
PATCH {{host}}/api/applications/1/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "status": "REJECTED"
}

### ==================== TESTING CHECKLIST ====================
###
### Run these endpoints in order:
### 1. GET / (Health check)
### 2. POST /api/auth/signup (Create admin - first time)
### 3. POST /api/auth/signup (Create student)
### 4. POST /api/auth/login (Login as admin - save token)
### 5. POST /api/auth/login (Login as student - save token)
### 6. GET /api/students/profile (Get student profile)
### 7. PUT /api/students/profile (Update student profile)
### 8. POST /api/applications/ (Submit application)
### 9. GET /api/applications/my-applications (View my applications)
### 10. GET /api/applications/ (Admin view all applications)
### 11. PATCH /api/applications/1/status (Approve/Reject application)
### 12. GET /api/applications/1/audit-logs (View audit logs)
###
### ==================== NOTES ====================
### 
### Authentication:
### - All endpoints prefixed with * require authentication via Bearer token
### - Get tokens from login responses and store in @adminToken/@studentToken variables
### 
### File Uploads:
### - For endpoints with file uploads, use the REST Client extension
### - Or use curl/Postman for multipart/form-data
### 
### Status Values:
### - Applications: PENDING, APPROVED, REJECTED
### - TAADA Flags: FIRST_TIME, REJECTED_BEFORE, ALREADY_FUNDED
### 
### Default Port: 5000
### Database: PostgreSQL (localhost:5432)
###
